<paragraph id="910318543DF34C02B64F9DD1827EE991" pageId="15" pageNumber="46">
<bibRefCitation id="3B7DC47104AA4A01E69ECF7DA731F7F8" author="Mitchell, TB" journalOrPublisher="Transactions of the American Entomological Society" pageId="22" pageNumber="53" pagination="1 - 44" title="A Revision of the Genus Megachile in the Nearctic Region Part 2: Morphology of the male sterna and genital armature and the taxonomy of the subgenera Litomegachile, Neomegachile and Cressoniella." volume="61" year="1935">Mitchell (1935)</bibRefCitation>
