<bibRefCitation id="587B868475B5E4CF0512123913982F08" author="Sheffield, CS" journalOrPublisher="Canadian Journal of Arthropod Identification" pageId="22" pageNumber="53" title="Leafcutter and Mason Bees of the Genus Megachile Latreille (Hymenoptera: Megachilidae) in Canada and Alaska." url="10.3752/cjai.2011.18." volume="18" year="2011">Sheffield et al. (2011)</bibRefCitation>
